<subSubSection id="B85C696870E4EF763D381B14FBE4C16B" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="description">
<paragraph id="D05FD787E409B52193A6351C27504CFB" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A41C37ADB217A597AEF3EB0050F75555" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Body (Figs 
<figureCitation id="CC098A4D38D464F9856723EEAC3DBF48" captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figure 1. Smaragdina hejingensis Duan, Wang &amp; Zhou, sp. nov. A habitus B lateral view of habitus C spermatheca D lateral view of aedeagus E ventral view of aedeagus F dorsal view of aedeagus G apex of aedeagus H ventral rectal sclerites I dorsal rectal sclerites. Scale bars: 0.5 mm (A, B), 0.2 mm (C-I)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1082.74323.figure1" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/634776" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">1A, B</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="4AD57274B51EDDB146C142A904AA4B05" captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. Smaragdina hejingensis Duan, Wang &amp; Zhou, sp. nov. A habitus B mandibles C maxilla D labium E dorsal view of aedeagus F lateral view of aedeagus G ventral view of aedeagus H spermatheca. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1082.74323.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/634777" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">2A</figureCitation>
) oblong, largely metallic blue. Mandibles yellowish brown, apex tinged with brown; labrum darkish brown; ventral side of mouthpart yellowish brown; four basal antennomeres yellow, others brown. Pronotum largely metallic blue, lateral sides with yellowish brown marking. Scutellum black. Ventral side of body largely metallic blue, prosternum yellowish brown, femora of hind legs tinged with black, last segments of tarsi and claws brown.
</paragraph>
<caption id="CB6E088442DDD9F4C730FE35F25903DD" doi="10.3897/zookeys.1082.74323.figure1" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/634776" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" start="Figure 1" startId="F1">
<paragraph id="CD20CEB1B35A3B35513D3BCE84269C5B" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="73CFD20875E31F0539595F50B65252AE" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Figure 1.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="6C9D2BFB0DD81ED64AEDFDDA9C7F2A5A" authorityName="Duan, Wang &amp; Zhou" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Smaragdina" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Smaragdina hejingensis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hejingensis">
<emphasis id="A8177FEF90F72A64755757A7110EC6D4" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Smaragdina hejingensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Duan, Wang &amp; Zhou, sp. nov. 
<emphasis id="6A6B9887F2C7B5095A21D966C2487314" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A</emphasis>
habitus 
<emphasis id="B371950B826998654186DE8C3AE48348" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">B</emphasis>
lateral view of habitus 
<emphasis id="F3FBD23A8A94221BD01FEB257C9B8D25" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">C</emphasis>
spermatheca 
