lateral view of aedeagus 
<emphasis id="DF89E1F52C89F0A82E1AD3748DAB8E65" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">E</emphasis>
ventral view of aedeagus 
<emphasis id="55EE294D671FDE7E04264B227BF44CCA" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">F</emphasis>
dorsal view of aedeagus 
<emphasis id="332A8718A5FFEC3B6AF6F5130292252F" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">G</emphasis>
